phrases: Yukako Yamagishi has been depressed lately.
I went to the Angelo Stone the other day and
there were a lot of tourists taking pictures.
Wow, it is that famous now, huh?
If I can just keep Koichi in my heart, that is all I need to be happy.
I thought that once, but it is really hard...
I wish he would look at me, even just a little.
But I just do not know what I am supposed to do...
My makeup will help you encounter love
I cannot believe such a wonderful guy proposed to me!
I guess a woman's youth is better spent
happy and ugly than dark and beautiful...
My makeup will help you encounter love.
What is written on that sign is true.
Episode 20 Yukako Yamagishi Dreams of Cinderella
I am the owner of this place and an aesthetician.
I talk like I have low blood pressure, but do not let it bother you.
But I am very motivated by my work.
I had no idea there was someone so beautiful in Morioh...
Now, please have a seat right over there.
Write your name and address on that form.
I have not decided that I will do this yet.

Makeup Menu Makeup to Encounter Love... 1000 yen Makeup to Capture Love... 1500 yen Makeup to Get Proposed to... 2000 yen Makeup to Make Men Submit... 3000 yen Makeup to Marry into Wealth... 5000 yen Makeup to Marry a Celebrity... 7000 yen Facial Menu
This salon is a bit different from ordinary salons.
I am an aesthetician who creates faces of happiness.
Physiognomythat is, the shape of one's face
If you have a face that will be loved,
it will heighten your luck with encountering love.
The shapes of your eyes and eyebrows are not good.
I am going to be blunt.
This is so stupid that I am beyond disappointed.
You are trying to charge money for this?
With that face, the more you love a boy, the more he is going to run away.
I have never had that happen in my life.
I am not very accustomed to working with CG.
This is the face that will encounter love.
This is a face we will create using only makeup and beauty massage.
But it only lasts thirty minutes.
If you do not encounter love,
I will return the thousand-yen fee to you.
Would you like to try it?
I have nothing to lose, so I guess I can give it a try.
Make sure you do not open your eyes.
My hands may slip if you do.
This is the makeup that will help me encounter love?
Will my luck really change just by altering
the lines of my eyes and eyebrows?
I-I have been looking for you, Yukako.
You passed by Rengatei earlier, did not you?
You looked really sad back there,
a-and I sort of got worried...
You were worried about me, Koichi?
A lot happened between us, but it does not bug me anymore,
so I do not want you to feel down about it.
Is this really because of the makeup?
why do not we find a place to sit and chat?
I guess I am a little thirsty...
I get to be near the cute, yet strong, Koichi...
I suddenly want to eat a chocolate parfait.
Does that make me seem girly?
That is what I wanted, too!
I am really on a roll right now.
My luck is really on a roll right now!
I can feel Koichi-kun's warmth and beating heart.
This is the happiest I have ever been.
I cannot believe it is this late!
I am going to head home.
Why is it only thirty minutes?!
Cannot you see the light's red?
It is the light's fault for turning red!
Why is it only for thirty minutes?!
You encountered love, did not you?
You should be satisfied with that, and come back tomorrow.
All of my other customers have done that.
I cannot stand luck that only allows me to be with
Koichi for thirty minutes, and then rips us apart!
Next, do the one that captures love!
You really do not listen to others, do you?
Cinderella was able to encounter a wonderful love,
even though she was bullied, because she had a pure heart.
Which means you need to have the willingness for such a wonderful encounter to occur.
Are you able to do that?
Just changing your physiognomy is not enough to change your luck.
I became an aesthetician because I admired the fairy godmother in Cinderella.
I want to live giving happiness to others, just like her.
You are very beautiful, and I like you.
So I will do this specially for you.
We are going to have to work on various parts.
must be transformed into a body to capture love.
And the willingness you need to do that is this.
You need to apply this lipstick every thirty minutes,
It is to maintain your body after I have worked on it.
If you can do this, you will have the luck to capture love for eternity.
The price is 72,000 yen for 24 hours.
Make sure you do not open your eyes.
I knew you were not a normal aesthetician.
I see... so they were Stand powers.
But the more I think about it, I do not care.
If you wanted to harm me, you would have already tried.
Cinderella is a Stand that transforms the body's image.
This perfectly completes the work on your body to capture love.
Yukako, your body has become invincible when it comes to love.
The pain in my stomach suddenly went away...
I have to go back and return it to her!
W-Well, I will see you later.
Do not you feel something when you look at me?
I am heading to the Kame Yu department store for research.
I was planning on heading home...
It is embarrassing taking pictures in a department store by myself, you know.
Was not I supposed to become the invincible heroine?!
No, Koichi's heart definitely belongs to you now.
But his reasoning is denying you.
Did something happen between you and Koichi in the past?
Oh, this gentleman is a manga artist?
Luck will eventually take your side.
It is almost been thirty minutes.
Make sure you do not forget to apply the lipstick.
Yes, I am doing it now.
Luck will take my side, huh?
You are going to Kame Yu?
There are even more of them!
And now the person I want here the least, his mother, is here!
Luck is on my side, my ass!
I will kill that salon bitch!
I guess I will start taking pictures here.
H-Hey, are you using the flash?
She is been startled, and the stress is making her disappear!
Move out of the way, please!
Our hearts are understanding each other.
Koichi's heart is flowing into mine...
And my life is going to change starting now...
What did she do to you?!
That bitch must have tried to pull something again!
It seems I have fallen in love with Yukako.
I am starting to think that her personality is not so bad...
It makes me feel warm inside.
Hey, Okuyasu, did you hear him?
Even a Stand would be blown to the moon if it heard that.
You do not have to cry about it!
I do not know what led to this sudden 180,
but if you and Yukako both have feelings for each other,
then there should not be a problem.
Yukako has refused to see me ever since.
She has not come to school for two days.
She will not answer the phone...
She has not contacted me at all.
Y-You mean ever since you guys kissed...
If anything, I admired Yukako for her dedication to love.
But honestly, I do not think you are going to
get an answer unless you ask Yukako in person.
We really should not get involved...
But if you are in danger, let us know!
I am going to go now.
I cannot believe he kissed a girl!
Seriously, it is no reason to cry.
You have got the wrong person.
You looked just like her from behind, so...
How dare you do this to me, you stupid dumbass?!
My face just keeps falling apart!
Even if I put on makeup, it just falls off!
Turn my face back to normal!
I persistently told you to reapply the Cinderella lipstick every thirty minutes...
I just forgot, that is all!
Your palm lines and fingerprints are disappearing.
You should not have broken the promise.
That lipstick was to guarantee your luck.
You need a lot of energy to change someone is luck.
And now that has gone away.
It is your own fault for underestimating your luck.
I am not running a salon for the sake of ambition and money alone.
I wanted to be like the fairy godmother
in Cinderella who brings people happiness.
I should not have tried to make your wish come true.
Your face and your palm lines are now gone.
They have been eliminated from this world.
There is no use for someone who is missing parts.
What kind of life does someone with missing parts live?
N-No, you have got the wrong person.
Dr. Aya, men are not allowed in here, are they?
Hurry and throw him out, please.
I sort of fell for that personality...
And that lady is a Stand user, right?
And she did something to you...
I will kill you, Aya Tsuji!
P-Part of her face went flying!
He was able to figure out that you were
Yukako Yamagishi, even though your face is different.
Even though you have denied yourself,
some people can see others' personalities.
On his behalf, I will give you one last chance as a fairy godmother.
Your last chance is to choose one of these.
Your real face is now gone,
but my Cinderella has memorized every face we have ever worked on.
Choose your own face out of these.
If you can pick your own face,
it is possible to return your face to normal.
Your palm lines and fingerprints will return naturally, too.
Just like Cinderella's glass slippers, pick the one that is the perfect fit for you.
You should have let me do that to begin with, you dumbass!
I can figure that out easily!
I look at my face in the mirror every day!
But if you choose someone else's face,
that face will never suit you.
In fact, speaking in terms of my own beauty standards,
I will warn you that your face will become hideous.
And your luck will be forever based on that face.
Remember, your face in the mirror is reversed.
The correct answer is that they are all wrong.
None of the faces there are yours.
If you can figure that out, I will fix your face.
That is my rule as Fairy Godmother.
Once I start second-guessing, others look like they might be mine, too...
There is no doubt about it!
I know, because it is my own face!
You will find out once you try to put it on.
My eyes look a bit more slanted.
I-I really cannot tell after all...
No, I am not going to choose.
You want to live your life without a face?
I am going to have Koichi choose for me.
No matter what face it is or what luck it carries,
so long as it was chosen by Koichi, that is all I will need.
I will not have any regrets.
I do not know why, but I have a feeling it is this one.
But if it is not the right face...
YOU-Um, use your Stand to hurt Reverb's eyes, and make me blind.
You said you would not have any regrets,
I am sure you will not want me to look at your face if it is not your own.
Because I have fallen in love with you,
I would really hate for that to happen.
So I think the best solution is for me to not be able to see.
It is because you chose my face for me, Koichi!
Who would have thought he would say
he would go blind so he could not see her face?
I bent my rules as Fairy Godmother a bit, but I fixed your face for you.
If I took the eyesight of a boy who has nothing to do with this,
my reputation as Fairy Godmother would be tarnished.
Yukako, it seems that you do, at least, know a good man when you see one.
Her makeup will help you encounter love.
